libvirt (1.0.0~rc2-2) experimental; urgency=low

  * [a2dd93d] Adjust systemtap build-dependency to architectures that actually
    have it.

 -- Guido Günther <agx@sigxcpu.org>  Tue, 30 Oct 2012 07:21:19 +0100

